<h2>Welcome, <%= user_name or "there" %>!</h2>

<p>Thanks for signing up for <strong><%= app_name %></strong>. We're excited to have you on board.</p>

<% if login_url then %>
  <p style="text-align: center; margin: 28px 0;">
    <a href="<%= login_url %>" class="btn">Get Started</a>
  </p>
<% end %>

<p>If you have any questions, feel free to reach out to our support team.</p>

<p>Cheers,<br>The <%= app_name %> Team</p>
